news_header: Global-E Online Ltd shares have surpassed the average analyst target price of $60.33, trading at $60.50. Analysts may react by downgrading or raising their target prices based on the company's performance.
news_text: Global-E Online Ltd (GLBE) shares have recently traded above the average analyst 12-month target price of $60.33, currently at $60.50. Analysts may adjust their target prices based on the company's performance, with some having lower targets (as low as $52) and others as high as $68. The average target reflects a collective analyst opinion, prompting investors to evaluate whether the current price indicates further growth potential or if it's time to sell.
